item.title: How do u change the place u start
item.dc:creator: @i_nelson_i i nelson i
item.description:
@i_nelson_i wrote:

log in to a new acc and type
::mypos

if u dnt have that command log out and open up char file and get co ords from there
now open up player.java and search for the x co ord and check if x and y co ords r same, if yes change them to what you want

also do this in client.java to change where u die etc
